OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FVariable
OL,6,Fcloud and brighter spells, with a few
OL,7,Fscattered showers Friday, these easing
OL,8,Flater. Breezy. Dry with sunny spells
OL,9,Fon Saturday and Sunday. Feeling much
OL,10,Fwarmer, with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
